Goals for this page:

- Be accessible only through a successful login
- Redirect to login page if accessed by non-logged-in user
- Allow admin to create MenuItems
- Display current MenuItems, organized by menu (lunch, dinner, etc.)
- Allow admin to edit existing MenuItem properties
- Allow admin to destroy MenuItems, with confirmation prompt

